{"word":"μεταπέμπω","slug":"μεταπέμπω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μεταπέμπω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ψω</el>) </el><p/><i>to send after</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:— <i>to send for, summon</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>arcessere</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; so in Med: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, aor1 <el>μεταπεμφθῆναι</el> <i>to be sent for</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/>"}]}